When accessing metadata for repository resource /2.0/repositories/{username}/{repo_slug}/src/{node}/{path} , the response body returns an incorrect commit hash and link redirects to a different file commit while v1 works fine.

Here is an example with a public git repository:

V1 REST API - works correctly:\\
curl https://api.bitbucket.org/1.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/src/HEAD/

{code}
{
   "node":"bd1b80394d8c",
   "path":"/",
   "directories":[
      "examples",
      "gradle",
      "src"
   ],
   "files":[
      {
         "size":172,
         "path":".gitignore",
         "timestamp":"2019-01-29T01:53:02Z",
         "utctimestamp":"2019-01-29 01:53:02+00:00",
         "revision":"c52652588292"
      },
      {
         "size":11358,
         "path":"LICENSE",
         "timestamp":"2019-01-28T02:30:28Z",
         "utctimestamp":"2019-01-28 02:30:28+00:00",
         "revision":"a25e64daa373"
      }
      ...
   ]
}
{code}

See "LICENSE" file has a revision of {{a25e64daa373}} representing a commit for the last change

V2 REST API - Commit data returned is not the same\\
curl https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/src/HEAD/LICENSE?format=meta

{code}
{
   "mimetype":null,
   "links":{
      "self":{
         "href":"https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/src/bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4/LICENSE"
      },
      "meta":{
         "href":"https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/src/bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4/LICENSE?format=meta"
      },
      "history":{
         "href":"https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/filehistory/bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4/LICENSE"
      }
   },
   "path":"LICENSE",
   "commit":{
      "type":"commit",
      "hash":"bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4",
      "links":{
         "self":{
            "href":"https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/gint_org/gint/commit/bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4"
         },
         "html":{
            "href":"https://bitbucket.org/gint_org/gint/commits/bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4"
         }
      }
   },
   "attributes":[

   ],
   "type":"commit_file",
   "size":11358
}
{code}

Note that the hash commit referenced is incorrec:\\
"commit","hash":"bd1b80394d8c495d3bccc9c74e275355ee5c78a4" and going to the html link redirects to a different file commit
